    public interface FieldReader
extends BaseReader.StructReader, BaseReader.ListReader, BaseReader.MapReader, BaseReader.ScalarReader, BaseReader.RepeatedStructReader, BaseReader.RepeatedListReader, BaseReader.RepeatedMapReader
    Composite of all Reader types (e.g. BaseReader.StructReader, BaseReader.ScalarReader, etc). Each reader type is in essence a way of iterating over a ValueVector.
